collectionMetadata.name: Total outstanding moneylending loans in proportion to the consumer credit market
collectionMetadata.description: Total amount of outstanding licensed moneylender loans taken in relation to/as a proportion of the consumer credit market, namely, the outstanding personal loans taken by Singapore households, including motor vehicle loans, credit/charge cards, pawnbroking loans, licensed moneylending loans and other types of consumer loans, but excluding mortgage loans.

datasetMetadata.name: Total outstanding moneylender loans as a proportion of the consumer credit market
datasetMetadata.description: Total amount of outstanding licensed moneylender ("ML") loans taken in relation to/as a proportion of the consumer credit market, namely, the outstanding personal loans taken by Singapore households, including motor vehicle loans, credit/charge cards, pawnbroking loans, licensed moneylending loans and other types of consumer loans, but excluding mortgage loans.
